  "response_text": "# Healthy Lifestyle Routine\n\n## Morning (30-45 min)\n- **Wake up early** at a consistent time\n- Drink water before coffee/tea\n- Light stretching or yoga (10 min)\n- Nutritious breakfast with protein and fiber\n- Brief meditation or journaling (5 min)\n\n## Throughout the Day\n- **Movement**: Walk, take stairs, stretch every hour\n- **Hydration**: Drink 8+ glasses of water\n- **Meals**: Balanced lunch with vegetables, protein, whole grains\n- **Breaks**: Step outside, rest eyes from screens\n\n## Evening (60 min before bed)\n- **Exercise**: 30-45 min moderate activity (walking, gym, sports)\n- **Dinner**: Light, 2-3 hours before sleep\n- **Wind down**: Limit screens 30-60 min before bed\n- **Relaxation**: Read, meditate, or gentle stretching\n- **Sleep**: Aim for 7-9 hours at consistent times\n\n## Weekly Additions\n- Strength training 2-3x per week\n- Social activities or time with loved ones\n- Meal prep for the week\n- Grocery shopping for whole foods\n\n## Key Principles\n✓ Consistency over perfection  \n✓ Listen to your body  \n✓ Stay hydrated and sleep well  \n✓ Mix cardio, strength, and flexibility  \n✓ Eat whole, minimally processed foods  \n\nWhat aspect interests you most?",
